               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="bold">HOW SUPPLIED
</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Hydroxyzine Hydrochloride Tablets USP, 25 mg are 7/32”, unscored, round, green, film-coated tablets imprinted <content styleCode="bold">DAN</content> and <content styleCode="bold">5523</content> supplied in bottles of 30.<br/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Dispense in a tight container with child-resistant closure.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at 20°-25°C (68°-77°F). [See USP controlled room temperature.]</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Manufactured By:<br/>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Watson Pharma Private Ltd.</content>
                     <br/>Verna, Salcette Goa 403 722 INDIA</paragraph>
